      "name": "class",
      "value": "chapter"
    },
    "innerText": "13. Terasamo paricchedo"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "Kārakapaṭivedhavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vedakassā"
      },
      "ti ",
      " sukhadukkhavedakassa. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tadāyattavuttīna"
      },
      "nti tesaṃ āyattā paṭibaddhā yesaṃ vipākānaṃ te tadāyattavuttino, tesaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Atra"
      },
      " imasmiṃ ṭhāne ācariyena parihāro vuccate. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kutoyaṃ tava tatthānurodho"
      },
      "ti tattha tasmiṃ aññassa attakārakassa abhāvepi sattusaṅkhātassa attano bhāvepi ayaṃ tava anurodho anunayo kuto kena kāraṇena ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "idha"
      },
      " imasmiṃ asati kattari kusalādīnaṃ atthibhāve kammavirodho kuto kena kāraṇena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Athāpī"
      },
      "ti aparo nayopi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kiñcetthā"
      },
      "ti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ettha"
      },
      " etissaṃ codanāyaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "kiñci"
      },
      " vattabbaṃ atthi, avasiṭṭhaṃ tāva brūhi, aparisamattā te codanā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tassā"
      },
      "ti attano. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kārakavedakattābhāvo"
      },
      "ti kārakavedakattassa abhāvo siyā."
    ],
    "innerText": "Vedakassāti sukhadukkhavedakassa. Tadāyattavuttīnanti tesaṃ āyattā paṭibaddhā yesaṃ vipākānaṃ te tadāyattavuttino, tesaṃ. Atra imasmiṃ ṭhāne ācariyena parihāro vuccate. Kutoyaṃ tava tatthānurodhoti tattha tasmiṃ aññassa attakārakassa abhāvepi sattusaṅkhātassa attano bhāvepi ayaṃ tava anurodho anunayo kuto kena kāraṇena idha imasmiṃ asati kattari kusalādīnaṃ atthibhāve kammavirodho kuto kena kāraṇena. Athāpīti aparo nayopi. Kiñcetthāti ettha etissaṃ codanāyaṃ kiñci vattabbaṃ atthi, avasiṭṭhaṃ tāva brūhi, aparisamattā te codanā. Tassāti attano. Kārakavedakattābhāvoti kārakavedakattassa abhāvo siyā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Atha na bhavatī"
      },
      "ti attano anāse cetanāpi anāso yadi na bhavati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paṭiññā hīnā"
      },
      "ti ‘‘cetanāya anañño attā’’ti paṭiññā hīnā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vuttappakārato"
      },
      "ti ‘‘attano anāse cetanāya nāso na bhavati’’iti vuttappakārato ",
      ". ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Viparīta"
      },
      "nti ‘‘attano anāse cetanāya anāso’’iti viparītaggahaṇaṃ siyā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Attā nassatu, cetanā tiṭṭhatu, atha pana evaṃ na bhavatī"
      },
      "ti attā nassatu, cetanā tiṭṭhatu, evaṃ gahaṇaṃ pana na bhavati. Anaññattapakkhaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "pariccaja"
      },
      " pariccajāhi ‘‘cetanāya anañño attā’’ti. Paṭiññā hīnā yassa so ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "paṭiññāhīno"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "Atha na bhavatīti attano anāse cetanāpi anāso yadi na bhavati. Paṭiññā hīnāti ‘‘cetanāya anañño attā’’ti paṭiññā hīnā. Vuttappakāratoti ‘‘attano anāse cetanāya nāso na bhavati’’iti vuttappakārato . Viparītanti ‘‘attano anāse cetanāya anāso’’iti viparītaggahaṇaṃ siyā. Attā nassatu, cetanā tiṭṭhatu, atha pana evaṃ na bhavatīti attā nassatu, cetanā tiṭṭhatu, evaṃ gahaṇaṃ pana na bhavati. Anaññattapakkhaṃ pariccaja pariccajāhi ‘‘cetanāya anañño attā’’ti. Paṭiññā hīnā yassa so paṭiññāhīno."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ubhinnaṃ"
      },
      " cetanattānaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ekadesatā"
      },
      " ekadesabhāvo natthi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Evañca satī"
      },
      "ti evaṃ ubhinnaṃ ekadesassa abhāve sati ko doso iti tvaṃ ce vadeyyāsi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Yaṃ pana tayā vuttaṃ yathā rūparasagandhādīnaṃ ekadese vattamānānampi lakkhaṇato aññatta"
      },
      "nti yaṃ vacanaṃ pana tayā vuttaṃ, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "taṃ"
      },
      " vacanaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ayuttaṃ,"
      },
      " nānurūpanti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tava paṭiññā hīnā"
      },
      "ti ‘‘ekadese vattamānānaṃ cetanattānaṃ lakkhaṇato aññatta’’nti paṭiññā hīnā."
    ],
    "innerText": "Ubhinnaṃ cetanattānaṃ ekadesatā ekadesabhāvo natthi. Evañca satīti evaṃ ubhinnaṃ ekadesassa abhāve sati ko doso iti tvaṃ ce vadeyyāsi. Yaṃ pana tayā vuttaṃ yathā rūparasagandhādīnaṃ ekadese vattamānānampi lakkhaṇato aññattanti yaṃ vacanaṃ pana tayā vuttaṃ, taṃ vacanaṃ ayuttaṃ, nānurūpanti attho. Tava paṭiññā hīnāti ‘‘ekadese vattamānānaṃ cetanattānaṃ lakkhaṇato aññatta’’nti paṭiññā hīnā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Evañca satī"
      },
      "ti etaṃ cetanāya aññabhāve sati ko doso iti ce bhavaṃ vadeyya. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘Acetano"
      },
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "attā’’"
      },
      "ti vacanaṃ, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "pubbe vuttadosato"
      },
      "ti ‘‘pākāratarupāsāṇatiṇasadiso siyā’’ti pubbe vuttadosato."
    ],
    "innerText": "Evañca satīti etaṃ cetanāya aññabhāve sati ko doso iti ce bhavaṃ vadeyya. ‘‘Acetanoattā’’ti vacanaṃ, pubbe vuttadosatoti ‘‘pākāratarupāsāṇatiṇasadiso siyā’’ti pubbe vuttadosato."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "780"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Atthi sattopapātiko"
      },
      "ti opapātikā sattā atthi."
    ],
    "innerText": "780.Atthi sattopapātikoti opapātikā sattā atthi."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "781"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Bhārādāna"
      },
      "nti bhāraggahaṇaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Bhāranikkhepana"
      },
      "nti bhāroropanaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "781.Bhārādānanti bhāraggahaṇaṃ. Bhāranikkhepananti bhāroropanaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "783"
      },
      ". Ekassa puggalassa ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "aṭṭhisañcayo"
      },
      " aṭṭhisamūho ekena kappena pabbatasamo rāsi siyā."
    ],
    "innerText": "783. Ekassa puggalassa aṭṭhisañcayo aṭṭhisamūho ekena kappena pabbatasamo rāsi siyā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "785"
      },
      ". Bho ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "māra"
      },
      ", tvaṃ satto iti paccesi, kaṃ saddahasi, ‘‘satto’’ti gahaṇaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "te"
      },
      " tava diṭṭhigataṃ, suddhasaṅkhārapuñjo ayaṃ, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "idha"
      },
      " loke satto na upalabbhati."
    ],
    "innerText": "785. Bho māra, tvaṃ satto iti paccesi, kaṃ saddahasi, ‘‘satto’’ti gahaṇaṃ te tava diṭṭhigataṃ, suddhasaṅkhārapuñjo ayaṃ, idha loke satto na upalabbhati."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "787"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Yo"
      },
      " bhikkhu imaṃ ganthaṃ accantaṃ satatampi cinteti, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "tassa"
      },
      " bhikkhuno paramā paññā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vepulaṃ"
      },
      " vipulabhāvaṃ gacchati."
    ],
    "innerText": "787.Yo bhikkhu imaṃ ganthaṃ accantaṃ satatampi cinteti, tassa bhikkhuno paramā paññā vepulaṃ vipulabhāvaṃ gacchati."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "788"
      },
      ". Yo bhikkhu ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "imaṃ"
      },
      " abhidhammāvatāraṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "atimatikaraṃ"
      },
      " uttamaṃ abhiññāṇakaraṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vimativināsakaraṃ"
      },
      " kaṅkhacchedakaraṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "piyakkaraṃ"
      },
      " pemakaraṃ sadā paṭhati, suṇāti, tassa bhikkhuno mati ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "idha"
      },
      " sāsane ṭhite ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vikasati"
      },
      " paṭiphullati."
    ],
    "innerText": "788. Yo bhikkhu imaṃ abhidhammāvatāraṃ atimatikaraṃ uttamaṃ abhiññāṇakaraṃ vimativināsakaraṃ kaṅkhacchedakaraṃ piyakkaraṃ pemakaraṃ sadā paṭhati, suṇāti, tassa bhikkhuno mati idha sāsane ṭhite vikasati paṭiphullati."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Iti abhidhammāvatāraṭīkāya"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Kārakapaṭivedhavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Terasamo paricchedo."
  }
]